h4. Current Behaviour

We can search for a page title and it will show in the search results (in the macro). Or we can use {{SPACEKEY:Page name}} matching the exact name to find it. There is no search results in the last case.

 
h4. Use Case

Similar to finding a page with excerpt include macro, provide the search functionality to be able to find pages from a certain space without having to match: {{SPACEKEY:Page name exactly.}}

